{{Quote|After a shift in the mines, Kedorzhans can't see squat for hours. You're "tall blur", I'm "short blur." If the news there start broadcasting your ''smell'', then you got a problem.|[[Marn Hierogryph]] to a wanted [[Zayne Carrick]]|<ref name="Kotor2">[[Knights of the Old Republic 2|''Knights of the Old Republic'' 2]]</ref>}}
The '''Kedorzhans''' were a rotund, [[Rodent/Legends|rodent]]-like [[Species/Legends|species]]&mdash;native to [[Kedorzha]] in [[Senex-Juvex/Legends|Senex-Juvex]]&mdash;who operated [[Mining/Legends|mines]] in [[SoroSuub Landing]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Taris/Legends|Taris]] in the [[Standard year/Legends|years]] prior to its devastation by [[Darth Malak]]. Kedorzhans had excellent senses of smell, but were virtually blind after hours in the darkness of the mines.

